{"tid":222156,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩茶客爭位掟茶壼 老翁頭破血流老婦被推跌送院","createTime":"2017-04-29T09:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T01:34:42.000Z","uid":3189,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42e36acc7d9061a952132d725e46ad73cf3cf5e0","tid":222156,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T09:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/zXIvCpQFWeFn_c_7qLdGTQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20170429a094746.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FzXIvCpQFWeFn_c_7qLdGTQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20170429a094746.jpg&h=71d90b42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩傷者一併送院。<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】葵涌新葵芳花園一間酒樓，清晨上演茶客爭位大打出手事件，要驚動警員，兩茶客皆受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n清晨6時許，一名老翁到新葵芳花園一間酒樓飲早茶，期間見有空位於是就坐，之後另一名相熟的老婦亦到，但慣常座位被佔用，同行老翁疑「睇唔過眼」出聲，要求該名老翁將物件拿開，讓回座位予老婦，雙方初時口角，但愈吵愈烈，粗口橫飛，混亂中，老翁將茶壼掟向對方，令其中一人登時頭破血流，老婦則被推跌受傷，其他茶客見狀立即報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場立即勸阻兩人，救護員為傷者包紥後送院治理，兩名老翁涉嫌公眾地方打架被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A9%E8%8C%B6%E5%AE%A2%E7%88%AD%E4%BD%8D%E6%8E%9F%E8%8C%B6%E5%A3%BC-%E8%80%81%E7%BF%81%E9%A0%AD%E7%A0%B4%E8%A1%80%E6%B5%81%E8%80%81%E5%A9%A6%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A8%E8%B7%8C%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2-013800920.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%258C%25B6%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E7%2588%25AD%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%258E%259F%25E8%258C%25B6%25E5%25A3%25BC-%25E8%2580%2581%25E7%25BF%2581%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E8%25A1%2580%25E6%25B5%2581%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A8%25E8%25B7%258C%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2-013800920.html&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=45ca5fb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A9%E8%8C%B6%E5%AE%A2%E7%88%AD%E4%BD%8D%E6%8